description:
Food came in a really short amount of time! Waited less than 10 minutes after ordering for food to come. Definitely recommend if you're looking for quick lunch or dinner because the food is quick but yet fresh and tasty. 

I had the pork leg stew. I didn't know what thai pork soup is and thought it was going to be similar to chinese pork soup but I was wrong, thai pork soup is much more spices and thick and full of flavor. I actually enjoyed this bowl of noodles. It had plenty of meat, noodles and vegetables. I am excited to come back and try different dishes. 

Bad thing that might have costed one star less was because they ran out of the taro in coconut milk dessert!!! I was so excited when I saw this on the menu, but sad when they told me they ran out);
